channel.title: (new rsps community)!
channel.description:
So I'm trying to gather a development team to make a brand new RSPS community unlike any other. I have a goal along with making it, and that's to bring the RSPS community back, and enlarge it. It'll support all bases including; RSC, 194, 289, 304, 316, 317, 474, 508, 525, 562, 639, 667, 704, 709, 749, 803 [EOC]. This community's website will have player written content, fast improvements, XAT chatbox, maybe a custom chatbox more cooler and more advanced. It's gonna be something that'll change RSPS history, and give more opportunities, and more tools for users advantage.
Message me for more info, if you're interested in being a part and helping out. thanks
